		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Speak to Caralee Grollo - S_GLO_IronThrone_Group3_Prisoner3 06d864d4-924a-4595-8155-d96df5b5f97e - (40; 39; 52)  in the Dock warehouse after saving them.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Quick setup:&#xD;&#xA;- Load CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Use Debug Book (Ctrl + Shift + 9)&#xD;&#xA;- Set Quest Flags and Options -&gt; Act3 (LOW) -&gt; Iron Throne -&gt; Change State -&gt; Back At Docks -&gt; MajoritySaved&#xD;&#xA;- Then talk to the NPC" />
